title: Life In Hollywood Is Not At All Like It Is In 'La La Land' | The Huffington Post
text:
Life In Hollywood Is Not At All Like It Is In 'La La Land' Here's the reality. But still as a musical! 
Comedy group Dr. America wants you to know that life in Los Angeles is not as it is in “La La Land.” But still, that doesn’t mean you can’t sing about the reality of LA! ALSO ON HUFFPOST Andy McDonald Comedy Writer / Editor, The Huffington Post MORE:
